description: Pomaire Boston Chilean Grill is taking delicious Chilean cuisine to the streets of Beantown and treating Bostonian taste buds to a food revolution. You’ll find all sorts of authentic Chilean dishes, such as Empanadas (baked or fried), Churrasco (grilled steak sandwich w/ avocado), Barros Jaspa (ham & melted cheese sandwich), and so much more, and of course it’s all delicious. So the next time you’re cravin’ tasty Chilean, make your way over to Pomaire, or have them come and cater your next affair.
name: Pomaire Boston Chilean Grill Food Truck
